{"tid":841171,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"出左劇場版コードギアス 反逆のルルーシュ Ⅲ 皇道 CODE GEASS 叛逆的魯魯修III 皇道","createTime":"2018-09-29T11:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T15:28:05.000Z","uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b33bbb294874f29111003fcf0647546fb6ab4e07","tid":841171,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/193132_ac0ba6c56966e27af546bc03c7f564ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F193132_ac0ba6c56966e27af546bc03c7f564ae.jpg&h=549fe6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n以被神聖不列顛尼亞帝國侵略而亡國的日本「11 區」作為出發點。立志粉碎帝國的黑色王子魯路修，與堅持公理的白色騎士朱雀所掀起的巨大變化。本次推出的三部曲動畫，是把過去的電視版再度編輯，並重新收錄配音和加入新畫面的形式所推出的總集篇。<br />\n官方網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.geass.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.geass.jp%2F&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6166ef5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.geass.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n線上<br />\n<a href=\"http://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/022/700/657/018e152b690a30ea679f03aa49abddf8_original.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fksr%2Fassets%2F022%2F700%2F657%2F018e152b690a30ea679f03aa49abddf8_original.mp4&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e5a49310\" target=\"_blank\">http://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/022/700/657/018e152b690a30ea679f03aa49abddf8_original.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nコードギアス 反逆のルルーシュ Ⅲ 皇道 特報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4jIMUpM4YN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4jIMUpM4YN0&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=83149b7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4jIMUpM4YN0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/193216_ed6721ba70d29b5165cd440f7a37377a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F193216_ed6721ba70d29b5165cd440f7a37377a.jpg&h=e9d7d598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事簡介<br />\n描述被神聖不列顛尼亞帝國侵略而亡國的日本──11 區中，立志粉碎帝國的黑色王子魯路修，與堅持公理的白色騎士朱雀所掀起的巨大變化。根據先前受訪的谷口悟朗表示《Code Geass 復活的魯路修》是描述零之鎮魂曲後數年後的故事。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n<br />\n監督：谷口悟朗<br />\n脚本：大河内一楼<br />\n角色原案：CLAMP<br />\n角色設計：木村貴宏<br />\n機動兵器設計原案：安田朗<br />\n機動兵器設計：中田栄治<br />\n機械設計&middot;概念設計：寺岡賢司<br />\n主要動畫師：木村貴宏、千羽由利子、中田栄治、中谷誠一<br />\n美術監督：菱沼由典<br />\n色彩設計：柴田亜紀子<br />\n撮影監督：千葉洋之<br />\n編集：森田清次<br />\n音響監督：井澤基、浦上靖之<br />\n音楽：中川幸太郎<br />\n配給：ショウゲート<br />\n製作：サンライズ、コードギアス製作委員会<br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.geass.jp/R-geass/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.geass.jp%2FR-geass%2F&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d8131814\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.geass.jp/R-geass/</a><br />\n<br />\n『コードギアス 復活のルルーシュ』2019年2月公開　特報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_4XGUWBng80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_4XGUWBng80&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=af68d600\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_4XGUWBng80</a>"},{"pid":"84b6780b7fcff231521cbf1bcb04354a8b823865","tid":841171,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"Shirley無死<br />\n有d位改左,so far 我覺得ok<br />\n不過有d位既歌,我覺得奇奇怪怪<br />\nShirley多左好多個shot,幾好既,無死<br />\n整體唔錯"},{"pid":"5d7ec00405fb8dd147836e62b31af001133e94e3","tid":841171,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"入戲院睇既<br />\n第三集改最少"},{"pid":"8e264e1f9ae109cc8de5396531178fa9c4f48497","tid":841171,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"係咪馬夫<img src